{"tid":1435470,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"〔極緊急！〕一人一信，反對購買大陸電，反對送錢俾大陸買核電","createTime":"2019-08-09T05:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:23:56.000Z","uid":98477,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc1bfc70a371806c2cb1c338ef184c1a1cfc957e","tid":1435470,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"各位好，小弟睇到巴打「半仙」搵到資料，話香港政府逼香港人買大陸電，並且想趁住呢排大家唔為意就暗渡陳倉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小弟極憤怒，想召集大家一人一信，反對向大陸買電！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟暫時set up咗個channel集中關注呢單case，希望大家入channel，人夠多再開group討論下一部行動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/noelectricityfromchina\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnoelectricityfromchina&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=aa13bbed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/noelectricityfromchina</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係「半仙」巴嘅post。感謝佢出力！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1429710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1429710</a><br />\n<br />\n=============================<br />\n<br />\n大家好，由於時間緊湊，政府最快要係今年年底向中共扑鎚買電防支爆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ys0TAxL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYs0TAxL.png&h=3e3fda02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為期三個月的《長遠減碳策略》 公眾諮詢係六月中已經開始左，無人理既話又會比政府陰陰濕濕過左，希望大家可以關注一下同埋花少少時間上佢個網填意見收集表格。<br />\n<br />\n但有樣野要注意！<br />\n就係一定一定要小心<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">問題三</span></strong>[/size=3]<br />\n三個措施係綁埋一齊答，<br />\n姐係<span style=\"color: red;\">包左同大陸買電</span>（更緊密區域合作），<br />\n千祈唔好中計！！！<br />\n可以係最後補充意見同反對向大陸買電 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9FTAs0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9FTAs0.png&h=0b301399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》獲悉，港府最快本周五啟動「香港至2050年的長期減碳策略」公眾諮詢，當局料提出與內地聯網買電方案。據了解，<span style=\"color: red;\">諮詢文件會用「更緊密區域合作」取代「內地聯網」字眼</span>。消息人士分析，一旦拍板聯網買電，未來香港或需向國企中廣核集團增購核電或可再生能源，本地電力市場利潤料也「送中」，中電和港燈業務難免受影響。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒指，兩電在香港寡頭壟斷電力市場，難以制約加電費。但港人亦反對與內地聯網買電，「香港好似澳門咁，靠大陸電生存，無咗能源自主性。」他認為，港府應先施壓促成兩電聯網互通，同時加強本地可再生能源發展。<br />\n<br />\n意見收集表格條link : <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[size=5]<strong>大家同我即刻入去填左佢</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/vcf.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.susdev.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fvcf.php&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=a35ca97e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/vcf.php</a><br />\n<br />\n黎緊舉辦地區討論坊既地點日子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpAkfqp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpAkfqp.png&h=86fff6d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190615&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20704587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190615%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20704587&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=add5f06a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190615%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20704587&h=c24dd94a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190615&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20704587</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/susdev/html/b5/council/SGPaper03-18t.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fsusdev%2Fhtml%2Fb5%2Fcouncil%2FSGPaper03-18t.pdf&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=7ec57bc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/susdev/html/b5/council/SGPaper03-18t.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/vcf.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.susdev.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fvcf.php&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=a35ca97e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/vcf.php</a>"},{"pid":"11f5aa13fb7785968181bf5454f268a478aca395","tid":1435470,"uid":98477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"推post!"},{"pid":"b4aa785f1687ec684763f7aa929b47b8bbb6c09c","tid":1435470,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e441b0457e9fb2bb069a9c39a2dd8472dff2c173","tid":1435470,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:17:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港，電力革命"},{"pid":"72951ce2d8e64a89eba3917daf9839cbe74f0dc4","tid":1435470,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，電力革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a573267e1076a637f2efa25f91415998c7220836","tid":1435470,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:48:14.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"32a0ea98bbfcd5fa55a06b73676d416f346c3ef0","tid":1435470,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:48:26.000Z","msg":"哩啲有用嘅post要推"},{"pid":"d38bdbcb0f9ee105ae893c75ef89fc32e7d23bd9","tid":1435470,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"幫推幫推"},{"pid":"29697b185